<Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Phase 2</Data></Cell>
<Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Useful in a later phase if the sandbox tool adds more advanced genesis or local network generation flows, because these compact specs are mainly shorthand inputs for generated starting-state configuration.</Data></Cell>
